BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:33429@somas.ouk.ac.ke
SUMMARY:MAT 851: March 2026 Special Examination opens
DESCRIPTION:[logo] \n\nFIRST SEMESTER EXAMINATIONS 2025/2026\n\nFIRST YEAR 
	EXAMINATIONS FOR MASTER OF SCIENCE IN ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE\n\nMAT 851: M
	ID SEMESTER EXAMINATION\n\nMARCH 19\, 2025                 TIME: 5.00PM - 8
	.00PM\n\n-------------------------\n\nINSTRUCTIONS\n\nRead these instructio
	ns before starting the examination. These instruction will be available for
	 reference throughout the examination.\n\n	* This exam consists of 10 quest
	ions\n	* You should attempt ALL questions. Marks for each question are indi
	cated alongside the question.\n	* All questions will be displayed in the sy
	stem and the system MUST be used to input your answers.\n	* Some questions 
	will require you to do the workout on a blank sheet of A4 papers\, then sca
	n and upload it in the space provided. We recommend you get  Adobe Scan TM 
	[1]  mobile app  on your mobile devices.\n	* The strict university examinat
	ion procedures must be followed.\n	* The Board of Examiners  reserves the r
	ight to disqualify all scores from  candidates if it determines that the re
	quired academic integrity procedures were not followed.\n\nAt the end of th
	e examination\n\nWhen you have completed the examination\, you must submit 
	your answers from the summary page.\n\nClick on the  Finish attempt"link un
	der the question number panel on the left hand side.\n\nAt the bottom of th
	e next page. Click the button Submit all and finish and then confirm that y
	ou wish to submit.\n\nFOR THIS EXAMINATION YOUR SCORE WILL NOT BE PROVIDED.
	\n\nPLEASE PROCEED ONCE EXAMINATION IS OPEN\n\n\n\nLinks:\n------\n[1] http
	s://www.adobe.com/acrobat/mobile/scanner-app.html\n
	
CLASS:PUBLIC
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T100817Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T160156Z
DTSTART:20260319T140000Z
DTEND:20260319T140000Z
CATEGORIES:MAT 851
END:VEVENT
